 3- wfy ḍyqtk dạymaⁿạ bạtḍạyq .. wfy ḥznk ạ̉nạ byk dryạn
 bs fy ḥby hạfk wạ̉bạrk .. whạnjyk ṭwl ạlạ̉yạm
 zy mạ ạbn ạ̉bwh bysẖylh .. ṭwl ạlskẗ lw tʿbạn
 ạ̹nt fy ḥḍny yạ ạbny mkạnk .. wfy qlby rḥmẗ wạ̹ḥsạn</lyrics>
